securityUserCheck()

Description
    bool securityUserCheck(string $username, string $password, string $type, resource $ldapConn, string $ldapDomain)
	Wrapper function for ldap_bind() with additional initial is_null() checks on $username and $password.
	
Parameters
    username
		String value containing a username.
    password
		String value containing a password.
    type
		
    ldapConn
		An LDAP link identifier.
    ldapDomain
		The name of the LDAP domain.

Return Values
     Returns TRUE on success or FALSE on failure. 
	 
Examples
    
See Also
	securityOUCheck()
	securityGroupCheck()